# CSS Margins

Margins create space outside elements.

## Example

```css
div {
    margin: 20px;
}
```

## Individual Sides

```css
div {
    margin-top: 10px;
    margin-right: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    margin-left: 20px;
}
```

## Centering Elements

```css
div {
    width: 300px;
    margin: auto;
}
```

## Real-World Example

Margins create spacing between sections.

## Summary

Margins improve layout readability.
